Hi I really appreciate the time you took to make this tutorial. I am having a issue. I am getting an "Execution failed for task ':Main.main()'.
> Process 'command 'C:/Program Files/Java/jdk-17.0.1/bin/java.exe'' finished with non-zero exit value 1"     error. Could you assist me please. Thank you!

#type vertex
#version 330 core
layout (location=0) in vec3 aPos;
layout (location=1) in vec4 aColor;

out vec4 fColor;

void main()
{
    fColor = aColor;
    gl_Position = vec4(aPos, 1.0);
}

#type fragment
# version 330 core

in vec4 fColor;

out vec4 color;

void main()
{
    color = fColor;
}

I followed this using on a mac and I ran into some issues relating to my openGL not being high enough level. After much pain, I found a way that fixed all the issues I was having so far. I added: 
'glfwWindowHint(GLFW_CONTEXT_VERSION_MAJOR, 3);
 glfwWindowHint(GLFW_CONTEXT_VERSION_MINOR, 3);
 glfwWindowHint(GLFW_OPENGL_PROFILE, GLFW_OPENGL_CORE_PROFILE);' 
to the window init function.
